{"tid":2159040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國 TikTok 禁令延期到 90 天後 同時要求之後必須銷毀所有美國用戶資料","createTime":"2020-08-16T05:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T05:38:32.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f04397b224cda6476da00fff5691b4dc70c1911e","tid":2159040,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:37:22.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯美國總統川普則是將原本限期延長至90天，意味TikTok將能有更多時間作準備。除了將限期延長90天，新一波命令更要求TikTok必須銷燬所有與美國地區使用者關連的數據資料，並且在完成銷燬後向美國海外投資委員會說明。而這樣的消息，自然對TikTok母公司位元組跳動能有更大彈性與微軟...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cool3c.com/article/155666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Farticle%2F155666&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=e6208ddb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cool3c.com/article/155666</a>"},{"pid":"2a5c573da5954ee86fcb313be9f70008a0136c97","tid":2159040,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}